.01798794,0.18033536,-0.01088736,-0.04046764,0.01725813,0.06176658,0.03670656,0.07648654,0.01797766,-0.02127946,0.00527168,0.07362501,-0.0314295,0.03657676,-0.01795124,0.01140934,-0.01885858,0.05857356,0.02207219,-0.05643486,0.02662169,-0.04893241,0.01604982,0.04740378,-0.02100544,0.05019466,0.02377489,0.05843733,0.04774654,-0.01764642,-0.0690667,0.01281581,0.00094851,-0.01230908,0.03757504,0.00643014,-0.03290522,0.00067703,0.01717018,0.06857351,-0.02412586,0.05261465,-0.03892444,0.0378861],"last_embed":{"hash":"3lpy5z","tokens":503}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"3lpy5z","at":1774917059153},"key":"2026-03-16 - Notes - 1Password Releases.md###What's new","lines":[20,1490],"size":158791,"outlinks":[{"title":"contact 1Password Support","target":"https://1password.com/contact-support","line":12},{"title":"#AUTH-2005!35083\r\n- If you load an empty `.env` file in **Developer** > **Environments**, it will now show a message saying no variables were found. #DG-7!35144\r\n- We’ve fixed an issue that could cause 1Password to crash when you signed in to a device. #PA-346!35258\r\n- We’ve fixed an issue that could block in-app updates if the MDM setting for automatic updates was enabled for MSI installs. #PA-941!35295\r\n\r\n- 1Password now supports a wider set of custom trusted browsers on Windows. #PA-901!34408\r\n- We’ve added a new developer setting to enable SDK integrations, so you can authenticate SDKs with authorization prompts from the 1Password desktop app. #39275\r\n- We’ve fixed an issue where a prompt to turn on two-factor authentication couldn’t be selected. #AUTH-160!34473\r\n- We’ve fixed an issue where the Windows Hello prompt could appear behind other windows or seem unresponsive. #DV-446!34963\r\n\r\n- We’ve fixed an issue where Windows Hello prompts could appear behind app and browser windows. #RO-800\r\n\r\n- We’ve Fixed an issue with an unclickable prompt when being asked to enable two-factor authentication during sign-in.!34473\r\n- You now only see the Windows Passkeys setup prompt if an unlocked account has the setting “Passkey item support” enabled. #FS-4434!34387\r\n- We’ve improved localization for a number of our supported languages. If you’d like to suggest a localization improvement, [contact 1Password Support","target":"https://1password.com/contact-support","line":14},{"title":"connect additional browsers","target":"https://support.1password.com/additional-browsers/?windows","line":41},{"title":"installed the MSIX version of 1Password","target":"https://support.1password.com/cs/1password-msix-installer/#what-to-know","line":52},{"title":"MSIX beta","target":"https://www.1password.community/discussions/1password/beta-release-new-msix-installer-for-1password-for-windows/155230","line":128},{"title":"too many authentication failures","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/ssh/agent/advanced#ssh-server-six-key-limit","line":159},{"title":"Labs","target":"https://support.1password.com/labs/","line":175},{"title":"See the accompanying article for more information.","target":"https://support.1password.com/kb/202408c/","line":338},{"title":"GetApp","target":"https://www.getapp.com/security-software/a/1password/","line":360},{"title":"GetApp","target":"https://www.getapp.com/security-software/a/1password/","line":397},{"title":"recovery codes","target":"https://support.1password.com/recovery-codes/","line":401},{"title":"GetApp","target":"https://www.getapp.com/security-software/a/1password/","line":417},{"title":"Unicode Consortium","target":"https://cldr.unicode.org/","line":472},{"title":"insights about developer credentials","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/watchtower/","line":499},{"title":"“Configure for WSL”","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/ssh/integrations/wsl/","line":517},{"title":"sign Git commits","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/ssh/git-commit-signing/","line":552},{"title":"security advisory","target":"https://support.1password.com/kb/202309/","line":613},{"title":"diagnostics reports","target":"https://support.1password.com/diagnostics/","line":630},{"title":"Contact 1Password Support","target":"https://support.1password.com/contact/","line":632},{"title":"contact 1Password Support","target":"https://support.1password.com/contact/","line":634},{"title":"use 1Password to sign in to sites","target":"https://support.1password.com/sign-in-with-provider/","line":656},{"title":"1Password Shell Plugins","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/cli/shell-plugins","line":698},{"title":"create the config file for the 1Password SSH agent","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/ssh/agent/config/","line":704},{"title":"secret references","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/cli/secret-references/","line":736},{"title":"supported sign-in provider","target":"https://support.1password.com/sign-in-with-provider/","line":835},{"title":"SSH agent","target":"https://developer.1password.com/docs/ssh/agent","line":865},{"title":"contact our business support team","target":"https://1password.com/contact-us/","line":985},{"title":"1Password 8","target":"https://1password.com/products/","line":996},{"title":"1Password extension","target":"https://1password.com/downloads/windows/#browsers","line":1099},{"title":"Trusted Platform Module (TPM) with Windows Hello to unlock 1Password","target":"https://support.1password.com/windows-hello/#manage-your-settings","line":1186},{"title":"Your CLI wish is our command","target":"https://blog.1password.com/1password-cli-2.0/","line":1199},{"title":"SSH and Git, meet 1Password","target":"https://blog.1password.com/1password-ssh-agent/","line":1199},{"title":"Screenshot of the untagged advanced search scope in action","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.10-untagged-advanced-search-scope.png","line":1288,"embedded":true},{"title":"Screenshot of the new Developer section under Settings","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.10-developer-preferences-window-coming-soon.png","line":1292,"embedded":true},{"title":"1Password Quick Access window with a custom collection selected using the new keyboard shortcuts","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.4.0.46-quick-access-hero-custom-collection.png","line":1298,"embedded":true},{"title":"1Password 8","target":"https://1password.com/products/","line":1300},{"title":"hear from you","target":"https://1password.community/categories/desktop-betas","line":1300},{"title":"saving QRCodes in your browser","target":"https://support.1password.com/one-time-passwords/#set-up-two-factor-authentication-for-a-website","line":1302},{"title":"An item being edited with a QRCode scanner icon shown on a one-time password field","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.79-scan-2fa-qrcodes-in-app.png","line":1304,"embedded":true},{"title":"An item list scrolled to the very end, revealing the number of items in the list","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.79-item-counts.png","line":1308,"embedded":true},{"title":"Quick Access with the account and collection selection open","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.79-quick-access-collection-selection.png","line":1312,"embedded":true},{"title":"Psst!","target":"https://blog.1password.com/psst-item-sharing/","line":1314},{"title":"The sharing window for an item showing who it is being shared with along with the new View history button","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.83-item-sharing-details-view-history.png","line":1316,"embedded":true},{"title":"The sharing history for my pie recipe after I shared it with my newsletter subscribers","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.83-item-sharing-history.png","line":1320,"embedded":true},{"title":"A Watchtower banner pointing out that an item has a weak or vulnerable password, along with a Change Password button","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.102-change-password.png","line":1324,"embedded":true},{"title":"Preferences window with new Appearance tab selected","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.102-apperance-preferences.png","line":1328,"embedded":true},{"title":"A screenshot of the sidebar with a tag selected along with a context menu with the Delete menu item highlighted","target":"https://releases.1password.com/img/rn/b8.5.0.102-delete-tag-from-sidebar.png","line":1332,"embedded":true},{"title":"Psst!","target":"https://blog.1password.com/psst-item-sharing/","line":1352},{"title":"Masked Email","target":"https://1password.com/fastmail/","line":1373},{"title":"Emergency Kit","target":"https://support.1password.com/emergency-kit/","line":1406}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"3lpy5z","at":1774917059153}},
